The ever duplicitous Nick Fury is amassing his own personal army for a Secret War, all while keeping his card close to his chest. Are his motives just? What lines should one cross for safety? How MANY LMDS DOES NICK FURY OWN! Join us as we dicuss Secret War #1-5 just in time for its 20th anniversary. We attempt to answer some questions whole raising many others in this fun discussion over a very post-911 story. Can YOU keep a secret? \*Rest in Power Akira Toriyama\*

